<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><aka>KoĘ»kda Xudo bor</aka>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Agar baxt va omad nurli yuzin olsa oĘ»girib
 Alp yigitlar suyganidan qolsa hamki ayrilib
 Ezilgan yuraklardan ketsa quvonch qayrilib
 GĘ»am chekmang azizam koĘ»kda Xudo bor

[V2]
 Ayni koĘ»klam chogĘ»ida qalin qorlar yogĘ»sa ham
 Nuh davrida boĘ»lgan toĘ»fon yonimizdan oqsa ham
 Orzularni sarob aylab armon kulib boqsa ham
 QaygĘ»urmang azizam koĘ»kda Xudo bor

[V3]
 Yovuzlar sirtmogĘ»i boĘ»yningni qiysa
 PoraxoĘ»r insonlar joningga tegsa
 Shayton yovuz urugĘ»in qalblarga eksa
 Shunda ham bilginki koĘ»kda Xudo bor</lyrics>
<title>Agar baxtu omad</title>
</song>